Package com.domino.app.model

Interface DominoModel

All Known Implementing Classes:
DominoModelImp
public interface DominoModel
The DominoModel interface defines the core functionalities and behaviors of the Domino game model. It provides methods to manage the game state, including player actions, tile management, and game settings. Implementing this interface allows for the creation of different game strategies and behaviors.
